                    "TitleEnglish": "Yamato & Terry's Excellent Adventure",
                    "SummaryEnglish": "Yamato goes onward to find Armada, but, on the way, Yamato meets Terry, who follows Yamato to find Armada, but, the two keep getting in fights. When they made it to Armada, they were given a test. The test was to draw circles & triangles all over the place, even underwater! A swarm of paper bats put their abilities to the test as well as learning Rapid-Shooting, but, what will Armada's next challenge be?",
