                    "SummaryEnglish": "Armada's next test is to knock down the statue of Armada with 100,000 B-DaBalls! At first it seemed impossible, but, later, when the dam was breaking, Terry & Yamato use the Rapid-Shooting technique to knock down the statue & save the town!",
